## Harness map

### L1 Context — what's always true
- [`docs/context/product/`](docs/context/product/) — vision, users, journeys, capabilities, success metrics, glossary
- [`docs/context/engineering/`](docs/context/engineering/) — stack, data, API, deployment, dev environment, security + privacy
- [`docs/context/design-system/`](docs/context/design-system/) — styles · foundations · components
- [`docs/context/conventions/`](docs/context/conventions/) — repo map + team norms

### L2 Skills — repeatable jobs
<!-- One line per skill. Keep brief. -->
- `skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md` — <one-line purpose>

### L3 Agents — sub-agents invoked by skills
<!-- One line per agent. Category folders: research / planning / generation / review / compound. -->
- `agents/<category>/<agent-name>.md` — <one-line purpose>

### L4 Rubrics — how we judge "good"
<!-- One line per rubric. -->
- [`docs/rubrics/<rubric-name>.md`](docs/rubrics/) — <one-line purpose>

### L5 Knowledge — what happened
- [`docs/knowledge/changelog.md`](docs/knowledge/changelog.md) — rule adoptions + structural events
- [`docs/knowledge/decisions.md`](docs/knowledge/decisions.md) — ADR-lite
- [`docs/knowledge/ideations.md`](docs/knowledge/ideations.md) — considered + rejected
- [`docs/knowledge/preferences.md`](docs/knowledge/preferences.md) — team taste
- [`docs/knowledge/lessons/`](docs/knowledge/lessons/) — dated event log

